  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "02b958b599a22536effc308f72772a2a13dd561d4da2f17636e5c744086c1d61": "Hello there, [?].",
    "0ac731a708e7c9b757e20ce95719cc9c7f5a76e4fbc53cd6e322f070b3649fd8": "Hello there, [?]. How goes the hunt for Lucien?",
    "0b0c36fe2797ce89796c7ff66d255da5cdcf95e6b2c392178b42d3001f2cf2ce": "Hello again, [?]. Good work recruiting those heroes. I reckon our task force is now complete.",
    "0ed95a2e8b84222922da0068edd4cce365a92f1c2f10f5e9a5e0845e54cfaba3": "So I take it you're [?]? I'm Idria. I've heard a lot about you. Much of it good... though it remains to be seen if that's enough to rectify your actions in stealing the Staff of Armadyl from us.",
    "1addc5f60a8dab3a22687eb82bc15e8813c46af1071835e24d7f7e8626afc953": "Ah, there you are, [?]. I have a new task for you.",
    "43c0a5b99b416bf1f839f199fcbac664a5f98b850acd8840feeff54825daff37": "So I take it you're [?]? I've heard a lot about you. It's a pleasure to finally meet you. I'm Idria.",
    "5416a23e353f5b7dbe95141212275f2aac03e1b4f98d59aa175345307eab71cd": "Hello there, [?]. How goes the hunt for the Dark Squall?",
    "665c33c757c5a5a28cd1b0322fbbc1429766fec55de22a893cbd2f26bfa7df63": "We're with you, [?]!",
    "67a405f5be1d54d7d7c8da1bbf1da775ad9ab2526e878c0687fa0c2f87b3a14f": "[?]! Thank goodness you're back. When Mazchna reported in, we feared the worst!",
    "7537c1c9beefedb002d30d9a6ce93b4a041d187b254f60a45213988c15275950": "You speak like you have first-hand experience, [?]. Surely you have not encountered this artefact?",
    "79101c535c7107ff31021ea67508a97201b4bcb459f146a5890d94f11ea3e484": "Hello there, [?]. Any luck with Movario?",
    "7bc234a0d863471190444809dec7cef798f9da95aa8e37af024af82ece0d31b8": "That was astounding, [?]! Good work!",
    "958e313c0478ac4c93884ba6e9a0d6dd692598b8e03ffa3cffeb4551b2f31a54": "Hello, [?]. How are things going?",
    "95e4cae81096ed1592c188e000bfadf8cb301d759f0b3a1bacc76cc21efe087c": "[?], you've helped forge an alliance between the Temple Knights, Crux Eqal and the Guardians of Armadyl. Three very different groups, all fighting for the common good.",
    "976e36e97d74e163c1b7e9dd85352020b63529d6b52ced4668b298d46c4c7d7c": "Hello, [?]. How are things going with that spy?",
    "b6a3a6f77bc8dfca0f7348f198f4fb2c362d469c6381e21aca9d846d8bb7a051": "Hello again, [?]. Have you managed to recruit those heroes yet?",
    "e05455bd082bf3de9d872cc4149b01620f3f4f9bf8881d390621a8e1a124dd95": "I thought we agreed to keep theology out of this? Besides, I'd say this work was exclusively [?]'s doing.",
    "ee3671483d37248a0bdce3b43a0de519e1861ed52ba380673c1e19c6bed0be2d": "They will never be forgotten, [?].",
    "f4d4696374d5c636b58478b0c8127078bedda0675a048eebba9048424e29c59c": "Don't worry, [?]. When the time is right, you'll be the first to know. I promise you, we will find Lucien. Together, we will stop him."
  }
}